title: LF Jungle Main for 5's must be Plat 2+
body:
^
We are looking for someone who will stay around and be dedicated to playing seriously

replies.body: add me im a jungle main been playing since s3 currently diamond 4 "Nubzy"

I've been maining jungle for about 3 season i know how to jungle most junglers, i was Plat 2 in season 4 but had a bad placement series and am now Silver 1
I hope that does not  effect your decision :)

I would be keen, just decided recently to main jungle. I got to p2 last season and currently p4, finished placements yesterday. Made plat playing everywhere. I don't mind waiting for your answer, not in a rush.
